# Noetfield www — anti-stale deploy (CRITICAL)

**Incident:** `.cursor/incidents/INCIDENT-2026-07-14-001-www-stale-deploy-overwrite.md`  
**Rule:** R-014 · MEMORY_LOCKED.yaml  
**Gate:** `scripts/nf_www_deploy_anti_stale_v1.py` · SSOT `data/nf-www-deploy-anti-stale-v1.json`  
**Universal law:** `.cursor/rules/000-noetfield-universal-change-preservation-law-v1.mdc`

## Law

**Live www is a deploy constraint.** Git `HEAD` is not automatically newer than production.  
A local uncommitted Cursor rule is **not** repository control until committed and gated.

## Forbidden agent moves

1. `git stash` (or clean checkout) of www WIP → `deploy-www-cloudflare.sh` from HEAD to “isolate” a small change
2. Redeploying full site from last week’s committed HTML while founder-locked live pages are newer
3. Putting **Investor** / `/investors/` / `/invest/` / “Invest in Noetfield” on `/`
4. Claiming “scoped deploy” when `www-pages-dist` still contains unchanged-but-stale homepage/enterprise HTML vs live
5. Treating `PASS_SCOPED_CHANGE` as satisfied by a local alwaysApply rule alone

## Required before production www promote

```bash
bash scripts/build-www-pages-dist.sh
python3 scripts/nf_www_deploy_anti_stale_v1.py --dist www-pages-dist --live https://www.noetfield.com
./scripts/deploy-www-cloudflare.sh
python3 scripts/nf_post_deploy_verify.py --expected-sha "$(git rev-parse HEAD)" --surface www
```

`deploy-www-cloudflare.sh` runs the anti-stale gate automatically after dist build.

